on`: persistent completion summary with explicit next/best and recovery actions.\n- `history_streaks`: reliability summary and repair affordance on wake dashboard.\n- `profile_settings`: mission-first section ordering then preferences, account/billing, help/legal.\n- `paywall_subscription`: transparent plan selection with explicit subscribe/restore and non-blocking close/maybe-later controls.\n\n## Behavior preservation notes\n- No auth/session flow rewrites.\n- No payment or entitlement logic rewrites.\n- No networking/storage/release config rewrites.\n- Existing wake state transitions remain in `WakeFlowViewModel`; UI changes only recompose/label controls and states.\n\n## Appium identifier changes\n- Preserved existing IDs:\n  - `wakeAddAlarmButton`, `wakeAlarmNameField`, `wakeAlarmTimePicker`, `wakeStrictnessPicker`, `wakeFirstTaskField`, `wakeAlarmSaveButton`, `wakeAlarmCancelButton`\n  - `wakeAlarmCell-*`, `wakeStartRunButton-*`, `wakeEditAlarmButton-*`, `wakeMissionButton-*`, `wakeDismissAlarmButton`, `wakeCompleteWakeCheckButton`, `wakeCompleteFirstTaskButton`, `wakeRunStateText`\n  - `wakeReliabilityRow-*`, `wakeReliabilityEmptyText`\n  - `paywallSubscribeButton`, `paywallRestoreButton`, `paywallErrorBanner`, `restorePurchasesButton`, `settingsRestorePurchasesButton`\n- Added IDs:\n  - `onboardingStepProgress`, `onboardingContinueButton`, `onboardingBackButton`, `onboardingSkipButton`, `onboardingStrictnessInfoButton`\n  - `homeNextCommitmentCard`, `homePrimaryActionButton`, `homeViewAllTasksButton`, `homeHistoryPreviewButton`, `homeSyncErrorBanner`, `homeEmptyCreateWakeButton`\n  - `wakeReadinessTonightSection`, `wakeReadinessLaterSection`, `wakeReadinessPausedSection`, `wakeCreateStepProgress`, `wakeAdvancedOptionsButton`, `wakeStateBanner`, `wakeFallbackExtraMinuteButton`, `wakeCompletionSummary`, `wakeCompletionPrimaryNextAction`, `wakeCompletionRecoveryAction`, `wakeCompletionGoHomeAction`, `wakeHistoryTrendSummary`, `wakeHistoryRepairAction`\n  - `profileMissionControlsSection`, `profilePreferencesSection`, `profileAccountBillingSection`, `profileHelpLegalSection`\n  - `paywallPrimaryValueHeader`, `paywallPlanOption-*`, `paywallCloseButton`, `paywallMaybeLaterButton`\n\n## Screenshot states captured\n- `reports/ios/screenshots/manifest.json` now includes required before/after entries for:\n  - `onboarding`\n  - `home`\n  - `primary_list`\n  - `create_edit`\n  - `active_task`\n  - `completion`\n  - `history_streaks`\n  - `profile_settings`\n  - `paywall_subscription`\n- Runtime screenshot capture is pending hosted iOS/macOS execution (toolchain unavailable in this Daytona worker).\n\n## Risks\n- `xcodebuild`/simulator execution was not run in this worker; compile/runtime validation remains pending.\n- Actual PNG screenshot files for before/after states still require hosted capture against the manifest paths.\n- Dynamic Type and VoiceOver verification depend on simulator pass.\n\n## Verifier notes\n- Pending independent verifier.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
