er key states including dark mode, Dynamic Type, and increased contrast.\\n- Extended token/component test assertions for new wake visual semantics.\\n\\nVerification status:\\n- `swift test` could not run in this worker because `swift` is not installed (`swift: command not found`).\\n- Evidence document includes command log, acceptance-criteria mapping, component inventory, accessibility notes, screenshot states, risks, and pending verifier note exactly as requested.\\n\",\n.workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/codex/visual-system.last-message.md:1:Implemented the visual-system scope in DesignSystem and wrote the required evidence file.\n.workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/codex/visual-system.last-message.md:7:- [visual-system.md](/home/daytona/workspace/.workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/evidence/visual-system.md)\n.workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/codex/visual-system.prompt.md:2:Stage: visual-system\n.workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/codex/visual-system.prompt.md:32:- Do not implement full screen flow rewrites in this phase. Only add the visual system and narrowly update call sites required to compile or demonstrate reusable components.\n.workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/codex/visual-system.prompt.md:40:Write `.workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/evidence/visual-system.md` with these headings exactly:\n.workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/codex/baseline-screenshot-capture.prompt.md:32:      \"phase\": \"before\",\n.workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/codex/baseline-screenshot-capture.prompt.md:47:- `phase` must be `before`.\n.workflow/iphone-app-ux-studio/research/reference-pack.json:74:      \"evidence_summary\": \"Fallback references recommend a single dominant interaction in mission-active phases and visible progress markers.\",\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
